node.text:
Leave a ❤️ if you try to eat HEALTHY.⁣
⁣
Eating healthy is NOT a COST, it’s an INVESTMENT.⁣
⁣
First of all, when you eat nutrient dense whole Foods as opposed to processed  you will get fuller faster with smaller servings. So you spend less money because you eat less and It’s not empty calories.⁣
⁣
Eating Healthy can seem like it may cost you more upfront but you make up those savings in doctors visits and decreased healthcare costs. Here’s what “sick care” can look like.⁣
⁣
Heart bypass surgery costs $75,000⁣
⁣
Dialysis - on average $86,537 per medicare beneficiary every year ⁣
⁣
Open heart surgery is about $324,000. ⁣
⁣
Liver Transplant Cost - $577,100⁣
⁣
Not to mention the cost of medications, also the pain and suffering of dealing with illness. ⁣
⁣
The pain of not being able to run outside, bend over, pick up and play with your kids ⁣
⁣
Because that right there is = priceless.

node.text:
DROP A 💯 if you FEEL this 👇⁣
⁣
I’ve spent several years researching the science behind the causes of various mental health diseases, depression being my most well researched.⁣
⁣
When we look at the data we see that depression is largely a disease of modern life. I say largely and not absolutely. I have also recognized that there are chemical and hormonal factors that play a role in mood depression, many of which can be successively treated with nutritional therapy and cognitive behavioral therapy.⁣
⁣
Therapies aside, the benefits of simply living in the NATURAL world as opposed to the DIGITAL world cannot be overstated.⁣
⁣
When you take an animal out of its natural habitat and put him/her in a zoo, you begin to see restlessness, anxiety, aggression, boredom, and depression to name a few.⁣
⁣
When you take a person and throw him/her in an office or school all day you begin to see similar traits.⁣
⁣
I’m not opposed to pharmaceutical drugs, they have helped many people, we should throw as much as we can at this devastating epidemic, however,  I wish we can get to the ROOT of this problem instead of continuing to treat the SYMPTOMS. Let’s turn off the sink instead of continuing to mop the floor⁣
⁣

node.text:
LEAVE A 💯 IF YOU AGREE⁣ 
⁣
it is said that the majority of a child’s personality development takes place from age 0-7.⁣
⁣
This means that who that child will be for 80 years is determined by these first few years⁣
⁣
I believe it is the same for your day. The FIRST HOUR of your day determines the frequency you carry for the rest of the day.⁣
⁣
The only thing I would add to this list is making your bed and working out. Accomplishing tasks in the morning creates confidence and that confidence/momentum will carry over throughout the day⁣
⁣
 Much love ❤️

node.text:
Drop a ❤️ IF YOU TAKE CARE OF YOUR BODY.⁣
⁣
Since your skin (your largest organ) absorbs what you apply to it, my advice is try not to apply anything on your skin that you wouldn’t eat.⁣
⁣
This Johnson and Johnson debacle won’t be the first or last example of companies inserting harmful ingredients in a product.⁣
⁣
Read the labels, stick with single ingredient foods and products and you pretty much can’t go wrong.⁣
⁣
Take care of yourself ❤️⁣
